data.description: Two story open concept floor plan with 5 bedrooms features a chef's kitchen with granite countertops and a center island. The kitchen opens up to the dining and family room. 4 Bedrooms are located upstairs and 1 bedroom downstairs. Private master bedroom with an oversized walk-in shower and closet and conveniently placed laundry room upstairs. Exterior features include an extended patio, shed and a full yard that backs up to a large green space, no neighbors behind you!
